'''詞中音消失'''（syncope）係話一隻詞中間嗰一隻音節或多隻音節拕跌吥嘍嗰情形。

==示例==
『[[英語]]』

*念詩嗰時間：
:''hast[e]ning'' > poetic ''hast'ning''
:''heav[e]n'' > poetic ''heav'n''
:''over'' > poetic ''o'er''

*非正式情況：
:''go[ing t]o''> ''gonna''
:''wa[nt t]o'' > ''wanna''
:''did n[o]t'' > ''didn't''
:''do[n't k]no[w]'' > ''dunno''
:''I [woul]d [h]ave'' > ''I'd've''

